@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/v1
@frontendOrigin = http://localhost:5173
@existingCategoryId = 1

### 1. Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

### 2. CORS preflight with Authorization header
OPTIONS {{apiUrl}}/reports
Origin: {{frontendOrigin}}
Access-Control-Request-Method: POST
Access-Control-Request-Headers: Content-Type, Authorization

### 3. Login as Ivan
# @name login
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "email": "ivan@example.com",
  "password": "Student123!"
}

### 4. Login as Olena for IDOR checks
# @name loginOlena
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "email": "olena@example.com",
  "password": "Student123!"
}

### 5. Users and categories for form/reference data
GET {{apiUrl}}/categories?limit=100
Accept: application/json

### 6. 401: reports require Authorization
GET {{apiUrl}}/reports
Accept: application/json

### 7. GET own reports
GET {{apiUrl}}/reports?limit=100
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}
Accept: application/json

### 8. GET own report details
GET {{apiUrl}}/reports/1
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}
Accept: application/json

### 9. GET own report with JOIN data
GET {{apiUrl}}/reports/1/details
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}
Accept: application/json

### 10. GET stats scoped to current user
GET {{apiUrl}}/reports/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}
Accept: application/json

### 11. POST report. Spoofed userId=2 is ignored; owner is token user Ivan.
# @name createReport
POST {{apiUrl}}/reports
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "userId": 2,
  "categoryId": {{existingCategoryId}},
  "title": "REST Client defense report {{$timestamp}}",
  "severity": "High",
  "description": "Temporary report created during the laboratory defense",
  "reporter": "Student"
}

### 12. PUT own created report
PUT {{apiUrl}}/reports/{{createReport.response.body.$.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "categoryId": {{existingCategoryId}},
  "title": "Updated REST Client defense report",
  "severity": "Medium",
  "status": "In Progress",
  "description": "The report was successfully updated through the REST API",
  "reporter": "Student"
}

### 13. 403 IDOR: Olena cannot read Ivan's created report
GET {{apiUrl}}/reports/{{createReport.response.body.$.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginOlena.response.body.$.token}}
Accept: application/json

### 14. DELETE own created report
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/reports/{{createReport.response.body.$.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}
Accept: application/json

### 15. 404 after DELETE
GET {{apiUrl}}/reports/{{createReport.response.body.$.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}
Accept: application/json

### 16. 400 validation
POST {{apiUrl}}/reports
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "x",
  "severity": "High",
  "description": "The title is intentionally invalid",
  "reporter": "Student"
}

### 17. Safe SQLi check: returns empty data array
GET {{apiUrl}}/reports/demo/safe-search?title=%27%20OR%201%3D1%20--
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}
Accept: application/json

### 18. Unsafe SQLi PoC: only works with ENABLE_UNSAFE_SQL_DEMO=true
GET {{apiUrl}}/reports/demo/unsafe-search?title=%27%20OR%201%3D1%20--
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}
Accept: application/json

### 19. Stored XSS payload: frontend renders it as textContent
POST {{apiUrl}}/reports
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "categoryId": {{existingCategoryId}},
  "title": "<script>alert(1)</script>",
  "severity": "High",
  "description": "<img src=x onerror=alert(1)>",
  "reporter": "Security student"
}
